 to make money compared to some other professions.&quot; <br>  <br> Outside of maybe enchanting Mining is by far the most profitable profession.  I say enchanting because this is probably one of the few end game professions that will always have a tremendous demand plus the money you make off melting is pretty good. <br>  <br> Z <br>  <br>  <br> <p></p><span class="SignatureTitle">-----signature-----</span><div class="SignatureText">Mordred <br> Zirella - Gilded Spear - Retired <br> WOW <br> Undead Priest - Active <br>  <br> </div></td></tr><tr align="right" valign="bottom"><td colspan=2 class="BoardRowB"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/post.asp?brd=22786&topic=85027955">Post Reply</a> | <a href="/active_topic_notify.asp?mes=85038717" class="BoardRowBLink">Active Topic Notification</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/pm_send.asp?usr=568053">Private Message</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/user_posts.asp?usr=568053">Post History</a></td></tr><tr align="left" valign="top" class="BoardRowA"><td class="BoardRowA" rowspan=3 width="17%"><a href="http://users.ign.com/about/dsanai?boards=vn" class="AuthorLink">dsanai</a>&nbsp;<a href="/Help/Faqs.aspx#stars"><img align=absmiddle src=/images/star5.gif border=0 hspace=0 vspace=0 alt="6,263 posts"></a><br><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><!-- WISH & COLL STUFF --><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr class="BoardRowA"><td nowrap="false" class="BoardRowA"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/collection/dsanai"><font size="1">collection (0)</font></a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/wishlist/dsanai"><font size="1">wishlist (0)</font></a></td></tr></table><!-- /WISH & COLL STUFF	--><span style="font-weight: bold;">Posts:</span> 6,263<br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Registered:</span> Aug 01<br></span><img border=0 hspace=8 vspace=8 src="http://media.ign.com/boards/images/icons2/other_smilingjerkle2.gif" width="80" height="80" alt="12449" name="12449" id="12449" class="IconImage"><br></td><td class="BoardRowA" colspan=2 width="83%"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Date Posted:</span>&nbsp;4/1 9:55am&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold;">Subject:</span> RE: A Complete Guide to Mining in WoW</td></tr><tr valign=top><td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">I also disagree with the statement regarding making money with mining. <br>  <br> Mining and Alchemy/Herbalism have both netted me a very good profit. <br>  <br> Your server may vary, but on mine, a stack of 20 Copper Bars goes for 45s-80s (demand versus supply drives it up to the high point occasionally, otherwise it generally is around 45s). <br>  <br> Since there is no cost involved in obtaining the materials you sell, and no cost to smelt (unlike Alchemy which has costs in the vials, and sometimes in the herbs if you don't have herbalism, or can't survive in areas those herbs are at and must buy them from the AH first), mining is 100% profit. <br>  <br> All you need is patience and perseverance. If you get bored running all over a zone, mining isn't for you. <img src="http://media.ign.com/boardfaces/3.gif" border="0" alt="wink" hspace="0" vspace="0">  <br> <p></p><span class="SignatureTitle">-----signature-----</span><div class="SignatureText">AC (Solclaim): D'Sanai, Monarch of the Emerald Order <br> Author of ChatCrayon, LootTracker, ScrollReader, TieTracker, FellowLink <br> Decal Plugins: <a class=BoardRowBLink href="http://www.emerald-order.com/plugins/">http://www.emerald-order.com/plugins/</a> <br> -=- <br> WoW (Whisperwind): Dsanai, Wolfherd, Mysterian, Feldar <br> </div></td></tr><tr align="right" valign="bottom"><td colspan=2 class="BoardRowB"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/post.asp?brd=22786&topic=85027955">Post Reply</a> | <a href="/active_topic_notify.asp?mes=85040935" class="BoardRowBLink">Active Topic Notification</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/pm_send.asp?usr=343566">Private Message</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/user_posts.asp?us